Three of its long duration programmes have catapulted the Indian Institute of Management, Bangalore (IIMB) to the top position in Central Asia in the Eduniversal 2015-16 Best Masters Ranking. Among these are the two-year Post Graduate Programme in Management (PGP), the one-year Post Graduate Programme in Public Policy and Management (PGPPM) and the one-year full-time residential Executive Post Graduate Programme (EPGP).While the IIMBâ€™s flagship PGP has topped the list for the eighth year in a row, this is the first time that all three programmes have made it to the top.